{"id": "1192911920961957938", "channel_id": "1192911920961957938", "type": 0, "author_id": "1112189464140324947", "author_name": "timee_ky", "author_bot": false, "content": "如题，在pve下无卡顿，pvp连续四五次出现匹配完成后卡住导致贻误开局选牌甚至直接因为未出牌而输掉的情况", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T19:26:05.189000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-06T06:57:07.650000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1193085827371257907", "filename": "B64B0950-FE66-444D-8CB4-7E0689ED2837.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 326619, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192911920961957938/1193085827371257907/B64B0950-FE66-444D-8CB4-7E0689ED2837.jpg?ex=6a00d503&is=69ff8383&hm=3d4736c6047e682bd12c8aa76378f017062b83c96b50f66ca8555997a9db4f1d&"}, {"id": "1193085827690008677", "filename": "F766D0B9-5C34-4EF3-9C9F-2C20FD6FFF1C.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 198187, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192911920961957938/1193085827690008677/F766D0B9-5C34-4EF3-9C9F-2C20FD6FFF1C.jpg?ex=6a00d503&is=69ff8383&hm=498f851225fd2c1680db33dcded1e9a971d81bbe1713fc603f9ebc3eb96f5d71&"}, {"id": "1193085828038152254", "filename": "18CB774D-C28E-4BC9-A239-74CADEA8446F.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 174065, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192911920961957938/1193085828038152254/18CB774D-C28E-4BC9-A239-74CADEA8446F.jpg?ex=6a00d503&is=69ff8383&hm=de55b38ae1d814f85b268ae5b6db1dc6a46faf72ea1751220e0e504a63ff5331&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1192911920961957938", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」关于pvp一进图立刻卡住黑屏或无法连接的问题。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
