{"id": "1192712880794107976", "channel_id": "1192712880794107976", "type": 0, "author_id": "1075686307910656000", "author_name": "fcg7698", "author_bot": false, "content": "伏于夜色的临时反击有概率不触发，我的菲因特装了伏于夜色，但有时打防御时不会加临时反击。下图就是，我打了两张防御以后，临时反击没有加。", "timestamp": "2024-01-05T06:15:10.315000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1192712881037394030", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-05-14-05-12-57_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 178604, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192712880794107976/1192712881037394030/Screenshot_2024-01-05-14-05-12-57_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=6a00cb2e&is=69ff79ae&hm=a78c1eafe3f852a4561881bca2773a7e62f8d72448e079204992884b39b73957&"}, {"id": "1192712881381322772", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-05-14-05-21-64_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 171238, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192712880794107976/1192712881381322772/Screenshot_2024-01-05-14-05-21-64_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=6a00cb2e&is=69ff79ae&hm=53b65e5d9a48c2d60680418bcfbda0f4ae1d297e8de91191cb4ac93901e58b40&"}, {"id": "1192712881729437766", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-05-14-05-38-53_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 163072, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192712880794107976/1192712881729437766/Screenshot_2024-01-05-14-05-38-53_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=6a00cb2e&is=69ff79ae&hm=a597d690d58616d0a810fb8aec89dc30b59c063a1b2c6acc0292c57740ee2940&"}, {"id": "1192712882031444058", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-01-05-14-05-30-99_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 161298, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1192712880794107976/1192712882031444058/Screenshot_2024-01-05-14-05-30-99_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=6a00cb2e&is=69ff79ae&hm=1d73ce0825162d84ce0350